{"tid":931198,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[最大贏家] 貿戰加速外資撤華 鴻海擬越南產iPhone","createTime":"2018-12-07T01:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T01:56:07.000Z","uid":141151,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f85f4ea58fb488a60fdc0163e0449bf93f9ba292","tid":931198,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:02:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">貿戰加速外資撤華 鴻海擬越南產iPhone</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2224074/%E8%B2%BF%E6%88%B0%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E6%92%A4%E8%8F%AF%20%E9%B4%BB%E6%B5%B7%E6%93%AC%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E7%94%A2iPhone\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2224074%2F%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E9%2580%259F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2592%25A4%25E8%258F%25AF%2520%25E9%25B4%25BB%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%25B6%258A%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%25A2iPhone&d=H4T%2BPylf5ae9qr21ynUjI0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=ab6ba425\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2224074/%E8%B2%BF%E6%88%B0%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E6%92%A4%E8%8F%AF%20%E9%B4%BB%E6%B5%B7%E6%93%AC%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E7%94%A2iPhone</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中美貿易戰衝擊下，製造業恐加速撤出中國。越南官方媒體報道，蘋果公司iPhone的最大組裝商台灣鴻海，正考慮在越南設廠，以減少受中美貿易衝突波及。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">分析：銷售不佳 外遷減成本</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n《越南投資評論》周一報道稱，鴻海與河內市人民委員會正在共同努力，擬在越南開設一家iPhone製造工廠，以抵消美中貿易戰的影響。同時，該報援引了越南工商會主席武進祿（Vu Tien Loc）稱：「我們正在與鴻海討論此事的可能性」。據悉，他已在11月22日的一次會議上向越南總理阮春福提出了此事。<br />\n<br />\n路透社上周採訪的多名企業高管指出，如果躲避貿易戰需要在中國以外地區建立生產基地、供應鏈的話，越南和泰國將是首選目的地，甚至不惜面對缺乏熟練勞動力和基礎設施不足的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此前有市場人士分析指，蘋果生產綫擬撤出中國，原因有二：一是iPhone一旦被徵稅，鴻海獲利空間勢必將再度受到壓縮；二是iPhone銷售不佳，毛利率和獲利都面臨相當大的下滑壓力，因此極需減低人力成本。<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>越媒：勢與三星爭當地資源<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n越南媒體也指出，目前越南是韓國電子大廠三星手機製造大本營，若鴻海真的要在當地設廠，勢必將與三星展開勞動力與協力廠商等資源的爭奪戰。"},{"pid":"538d33f7553b31d753dd9747cfd6ccd583e71a67","tid":931198,"uid":997,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:08:32.000Z","msg":"東南亞或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"ee3fbd38321805a8b595e84d371d9d75095700ff","tid":931198,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:10:29.000Z","msg":"等睇供唔切貨"},{"pid":"50dcbdc264352cde753748baa213a158aedf8851","tid":931198,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:38:20.000Z","msg":"越仔泰仔唔爭氣啫，懶到出汁，勤力啲既一早撤左過去"},{"pid":"ff9d767ec5db2f8010e57842d55587b49e762d62","tid":931198,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:49:14.000Z","msg":"打落水狗，東南亞列弱國家，割吞中共利益"},{"pid":"a76c3d6cbf155973b925062c23d2b2279a57509a","tid":931198,"uid":150347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ee3fbd38321805a8b595e84d371d9d75095700ff","tid":931198,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:10:29.000Z","msg":"等睇供唔切貨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:56:28.000Z","msg":"你睇XS XS MAX XSR個售量就知Apple家陣個倉幾多貨未岀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慢慢搬到岀年中都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e4b951efb07c93bf45d25f983651d8075ec510","tid":931198,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a7d6aa659f849ee3554e4e4785c20b1fad366f","tid":931198,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee3fbd38321805a8b595e84d371d9d75095700ff","tid":931198,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:10:29.000Z","msg":"等睇供唔切貨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T11:20:43.000Z","msg":"用下腦啦，5毛<br />\n大把貨都賣唔出"},{"pid":"2e9f2e325ed3169a05cb6006af282b9f67d633ad","tid":931198,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T0